+!~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
+!       NASA/GSFC, Data Assimilation Office, Code 910.3, GEOS/DAS      !
+!BOP -------------------------------------------------------------------
+!
+! !IROUTINE: getall_ - Return all Items from a List as one String
+!
+! !DESCRIPTION:
