+!~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
+!       NASA/GSFC, Data Assimilation Office, Code 910.3, GEOS/DAS      !
+!BOP -------------------------------------------------------------------
+!
+! !IROUTINE: initc_ - Create a String using a CHARACTER
+!
+! !DESCRIPTION:
