+!
+! !IROUTINE: inits_ - Initialization of a String from another String
+!
+! !DESCRIPTION:
+! This routine takes an input {\tt String} argument {\tt iStr} and 
+! creates an output {\tt String} argument {\tt oStr}.  In other words,
