+!
+! !IROUTINE: clean_ - Deallocate Memory Occupied by a String
+!
+! !DESCRIPTION:
+! This routine deallocates memory associated with the input/output 
+! {\tt String} argument {\tt str}.  This amounts to deallocating 
+! {\tt str\%c}.
